
Skills enhace your fighting ability. A certian skill is used when a weapon
can be used by wielding one of the names to the right of the skill name.
Shield is used with all armours of type shield.

sword:   sword, swords, blade, blades, katana
knife:   knife, dagger
polearm: polearm, spear, trident, stick, pole
bow:     bow, gun
club:    club, hammer, staff, mace, morningstar
axe:     axe
